br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"ded424d0f445ab17343822bdf8e65d4292ed4b81","tid":1491973,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"誓詞:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjSD2xA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjSD2xA.png&h=05f2943e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f66f259d024160f187b6097f2f7907e2bb3f4671","tid":1491973,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"881918b5d1c64ef2bcc066aec93655c463c82c20","tid":1491973,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353de8ebbf647388cd281ae4b1c3b8e44590bc17","tid":1491973,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"推，全隊破產"},{"pid":"55e0c603749b49d9f78d4beb3302af9f063e92af","tid":1491973,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"一切嘢都要以解散警隊做step1<br />\n<br />\n而家所有調查都係好似7警案咁，一路受薪一路查<br />\n大家覺得合理？"},{"pid":"41c51489eb322a4a8618ca7e7f5ba61b834413d8","tid":1491973,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"追到黑警破產跳樓"},{"pid":"1fa07804b0d4e826a384798ff656dc7b3d7bc1f0","tid":1491973,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e0c603749b49d9f78d4beb3302af9f063e92af","tid":1491973,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"一切嘢都要以解散警隊做step1<br />\n<br />\